{"tid":2508522,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美聯邦調查人員到Trump私人律師 朱利亞尼寓所及辦公室蒐證","createTime":"2021-04-28T23:19:48.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-29T00:54:46.000Z","uid":141151,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"b17197db3c2bc5200f0676fb5def71dc35945d8c","tid":2508522,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T23:19:48.000Z","msg":"美聯邦調查人員到朱利亞尼寓所及辦公室蒐證<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1588304-20210429.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1588304-20210429.htm&d=DgCTbN7XbHZJJfbPUwNNzSwbHaueoKb2XZOoGTcnCr8%3D&h=2b03084b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1588304-20210429.htm&h=d74d07ab\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1588304-20210429.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n美國聯邦調查人員，到前總統特朗普的私人律師朱利亞尼的寓所及辦公室蒐證。<br />\n<br />\n調查人員說今次蒐證，是針對朱利亞尼與烏克蘭之間交易的調查行動一部分。報道指當局一直調查，在試圖令烏克蘭官員，尋找特朗普去年大選對手拜登的政治黑材料方面，朱利亞尼所扮演的角色；拜登在大選擊敗爭取連任的特朗普，當選總統。<br />\n<br />\n搜查令在當地星期三執行，由聯邦法官簽署，賦予調查人員權力，到朱利亞尼在紐約市曼哈頓區麥迪遜大道的寓所，以及他在公園大道的辦公室蒐證。紐約時報報道，調查人員帶走一些電子器材。"},{"pid":"15b7da166d4c84ff27e7e78f21485b2640a1e935","tid":2508522,"uid":237465,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T23:47:51.000Z","msg":"美民豬黨又想搞鳩人"},{"pid":"c1c8d4792793a50775211a077808af694d78e7b0","tid":2508522,"uid":265839,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T23:49:24.000Z","msg":"政治清算"},{"pid":"b3a930480be86a08925d14d356a1539c5c960cab","tid":2508522,"uid":256837,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T23:54:46.000Z","msg":"hunter?<br />\n<br />\nFbi：睇唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b2bf0717fed6f6b6056c0710da19283f902ccc7","tid":2508522,"uid":292710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b3a930480be86a08925d14d356a1539c5c960cab","tid":2508522,"uid":256837,"l